metadata.name: Endless Personalities Catharsis #Sally
metadata.description:
This 5th chapter is about a kaleidoscope of different personalities used and shown in front of the public. All shot as ID pictures, it’s questioning about self identity and evolution through a lifetime.


Sally is a friend, wife, lover, mother, sister and muse. Generous and sensitive to the needs of others, she cares and nurtures the untoxic loving people around her. She doesn't hesitate to give without expecting a return back as much for material goods as for her time. Time, the most precious thing for her.




FR : Sally est une amie, amoureuse, femme, mère, soeur, muse. Généreuse et attentive, elle prend soin des personnes aimantes et bienveillantes autour d'elle et n'hésite pas à donner sans attendre en retour autant pour les biens matériels que pour son temps. Le temps, la chose la plus précieuse à ses yeux.
